      "span_text": "Unfortunately, the time needed to assess mental health issues is too often delayed or deferred until a crisis event occurs. [CITATION_1] 15 The American Nurses Association has said that ''the strength and promise of technology lie in providing increased access to health care services by augmenting existing services, not replacing them.'' 16 An eScreening tool that could quickly screen for alcohol abuse and depression might be very useful in supplementing routine intake assessments.",
